TextEng: You're a potential threat, so you can rot here.
Oh, what the hell. I'll see what I can do.
Text: 에라 모르겠다. 뭐 할 수 있는지 알아보지.

TextEng: I am leaving. What should I do about you, hmm?
Text: 난 간다. 너는 어떻게 처리해야 할까, 흠?

TextEng: Cease your raving!
Relax, I will help, but I have some questions.
Text: 진정해, 도와줄게. 하지만 질문이 좀 있어.

TextEng: You relax. Me help, but gots questions first.
Text: 진정해. 도와줄게, 근데 질문 먼저 있어.

TextEng: Shut up or me leave you.
Me leave. What me do about you, hmm?
Text: 나 간다. 나 너 어쩌면 돼, 흠?

TextEng: Whatever. Me see what me can do.
Text: 뭐 어때. 나 할 수 있는 거 해볼게.

TextEng: You rot here 'cause you maybe be dangerous later.
Text: 너 나중에 위험할지도 몰라. 여기서 썩어.

TextEng: Who are you?
Who you?
Scaled Worm? What do you mean?
What you mean, Scaled Worm?
How did you end up in here?
How you get put in here?
What do you think this Gulnan is?
What you think Gulnan is?
Where is she?
Where she go?
Back to my other questions.
Back to other questions, okay?
You would defeat her if released? She already beat you.
Text: 풀려나면 그녀를 물리칠 수 있다고? 이미 한 번 졌잖아.

TextEng: You defeat her if released? She beat you already once.
Text: 풀려나면 그녀 물리쳐? 벌써 한 번 졌잖아.

TextEng: What god does she sacrifice to?
What god she kill stuff for?
Focus? What do you mean?
What you mean by focus thing?
Foul minion of darkness, you'll stay imprisoned here.
Text: 사악한 어둠의 졸개야, 넌 여기 갇혀 있어라.

TextEng: You bad, so you stay here like in jail.
Text: 너 나빠. 그러니 여기 감옥처럼 있어.
